Package: fundiversity
Title: Easy Computation of Functional Diversity Indices
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    c(
      person("Matthias", "Grenié",
        email = "matthias.grenie@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4659-7522")),
      person("Hugo", "Gruson",
        role = "aut",
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4094-1476"))
    )
Description: Computes 4 functional diversity indices: Functional Divergence
  FDiv, Function Evenness Feve, Fonctional Richness FRic, and Rao's entropy Q 
  (reviewed in Villéger et al. 2008 <doi:10.1890/07-1206.1>). Provides
  efficient and modular functions to compute functional diversity indices.
